== International relations ==
=== Twin towns – sister cities===
Cosenza is twinned with:
* Kenosha, Wisconsin, United States, since 1979
* Lansing, Michigan, United States, since 2000
* Sault Ste. Marie, Ontario, Canada, since 2010

